{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView","text":"MLNMapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"mapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"annotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)UIControl","text":"UIControl"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"control"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The map view containing the specified annotation.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"mapView"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The annotation whose accessory view was tapped."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"annotation"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The control that was tapped.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"control"}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In a standard callout view, accessory views contain custom content and are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"positioned on either side of the annotation title text. If an accessory view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you specify is a descendant of the "},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" class, the map view calls this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method as a convenience whenever the user taps your view. You can use this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method to respond to taps and perform any actions associated with that control."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example, if your control displays additional information about the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation, you could use this method to present a modal panel with that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your custom accessory views are not descendants of the "},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" class,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the map view does not call this method. If the annotation has a custom callout"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view via the "},{"code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method, you can specify the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"custom accessory views using the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"leftAccessoryView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"rightAccessoryView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" properties.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":4,"anchor":"Related-examples","text":"Related examples","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to trigger an action when the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"standard callout bubble’s accessory control is tapped."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"schema